<div class="mod mod-text" id="498028973">
    
        
        
            <article class="clearfix">
                
                    <h2>The FOEN in numbers&nbsp;</h2>
<p>In 2022, the FOEN has a workforce of around 528 FTE (full time equivalent) to carry out its work. It administers a budget of approximately CHF 1.9 billion. This corresponds to around 2.4 percent of the total federal budget. Approximately 89 percent of these funds are used for subsidies and the redistribution of incentive levies (CO2 and VOC). 11 percent is spent on personnel, material and operating costs.</p>

                
                
            </article>
        
    
